e_banner\":[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null],\"localized_sale_logo\":[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null],\"sale_font\":\"\",\"sale_background_color\":\"\",\"sale_header_offset\":530,\"referenced_appids\":[],\"bBroadcastEnabled\":false,\"broadcastChatSetting\":\"hide\",\"default_broadcast_title\":\"#Broadcast_default_title_dev\",\"localized_broadcast_title\":[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null],\"localized_broadcast_left_image\":[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null],\"localized_broadcast_right_image\":[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null],\"broadcast_whitelist\":[],\"bScheduleEnabled\":false,\"scheduleEntries\":[]}","announcement_body":{"gid":"506226349467240139","clanid":"44156989","posterid":"0","headline":"Into the Unjust: 6.0.1","posttime":1770113379,"updatetime":1770379621,"body":"[p]*** INCOMING MESSAGE FROM HIGH COMMAND ***[\/p][p]We have confirmed, with concrete proof and beyond any doubt, that the Automaton Collective stole our schematics for the Star of Peace. We cannot let them turn this defensive tool of peace into a destructive weapon of war. It's now up to you, our most elite and powerful force, to bring them to justice on their own turf.[\/p][p]\n[\/p][p]We have approved the deployment of new equipment for squads to aid in the swift elimination of the Automaton threat.[\/p][p]\n[\/p][p]Push toward Cyberstan and end this insult to Managed Democracy. Helldivers, let this be the last time the Automatons steal from Super Earth.[\/p][p]\n[\/p][h2]\ud83d\udccd [b]Patch Highlights[\/b][\/h2][p]\n[img src=\"{STEAM_CLAN_IMAGE}\/44156989\/3d91c6650b5f4b1f6e7a528bf4cc9c37e11cb2c6.jpg\"][\/img][\/p][list][*][p]Bastion Tank: A new tank vehicle is ready to roll over entrenched enemies! The Bastion Tank offers unrivaled firepower and defense on the battlefield. It will require your team to work together to hunt down the enemy! (2pm CET)[\/p][\/*][*][p]Chinese VO has been added to Helldivers 2![\/p][\/*][*][p]Arm yourself with the latest premium Warbond* Siegebreakers, loaded with a devastating hammer built for close-range persuasion and an upgrade to a [i]Helldivers [\/i]favorite, the LAS-16 Trident![\/p][\/*][*][p]March into battle in style with the new War Horse set, available in the Superstore on February 10![\/p][\/*][*][p]With a few exceptions, all victory poses and emotes are now interchangeable![\/p][\/*][\/list][p]\n[\/p][h2]\u2696\ufe0f [b]Balancing\n[\/b][\/h2][p][\/p][h3][b]General changes overview[\/b][\/h3][p]\n[\/p][p]Melee weapons and Armor passive with increased melee damage re-balance[\/p][p][\/p][list][*][p]Intent is to make the Armor passive that increases melee damage less mandatory but still be useful to make melee weapons more effective.[\/p][\/*][*][p]We increased all the melee weapons damage and decreased the modifiers on the armor passives that increase melee damage.[\/p][\/*][\/list][list][*][p]Total damage with the melee armor passive will be higher or the same as before.[\/p][\/*][\/list][list][*][p]Base melee attack also got a 50% damage increase.[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][\/p][p]SMG and Pistol rounds less Sway[\/p][p][\/p][list][*][p]The intent is that the increased drag of SMG and Pistol which make it a close combat weapon and less effective at range is the main characteristic of these weapons.[\/p][\/*][*][p]We decreased the Sway modifier to be the same as most other weapons[\/p][\/*][\/list][p]\n[\/p][p]Unify Weapon function directions inputs[\/p][p][\/p][list][*][p]The intent is to make the \"weapon function modes\" that are similar to be on the same \"weapon function direction input\".[\/p][\/*][*][p]This is to make it easier to remember which direction similar types of weapon functions are and also make it so you need to use less \"quick weapon functions\" inputs.[\/p][\/*][*][p]Weapon function modes that affect Programmable ammo, Ammo types, Volley modes, Safe modes, Guided modes will now be in the left direction.\u00a0[\/p][\/*][*][p]We have not moved the underbarrel weapon switching option to the left yet, but we are looking into moving it to the left direction so all ammo altering switching is in the left direction even if it is an underbarrel selection that usually is in the down direction.[\/p][\/*][\/list][p]\nDifficulty on difficulty 9+[\/p][p]\nMade changes across all factions to increase the intensity on high difficulties, the biggest change should be noticed on the Automaton front while Terminids and the Illuminate are less affected.[\/p][p]\n[\/p][h3][b]Value changes[\/b][\/h3][h3][b]\n[\/b][\/h3][h3][b]Primary weapons[\/b][\/h3][p][\/p][p][b]R-2124 Constitution[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Increased Bayonet melee damage from 110 to 165[\/p][\/*][*][p]Increased Bayonet melee durable damage from 55 to 83[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]R-2 Amendment[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Increased Bayonet melee damage from 110 to 165[\/p][\/*][*][p]Increased Bayonet melee durable damage from 55 to 83[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]MP-98 Knight[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Decreased sway modifier from 1.2 to 1[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]SMG-37 Defender[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Decreased sway modifier from 1.2 to 1[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]SMG-72 Pummeler[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Decreased sway modifier from 1.2 to 1[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]M7S SMG[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Decreased sway modifier from 1.2 to 1[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]SG-20 Halt[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Move the \u201cammo type\u201d weapon function from Right to Left weapon function direction[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]DBS-2 Double Freedom[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Move the \u201cVolley\/Semi mode\u201d weapon function from Right to Left weapon function direction [\/p][\/*][\/list][p][\/p][h3][b]Sidearms weapons[\/b]\n[\/h3][p][b]P-72 Crisper[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Increased magazine capacity from 30 to 50[\/p][\/*][*][p]Decreased sway modifier from 1.2 to 1[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]P-2 Peacemaker[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Decreased sway modifier from 1.2 to 1[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]LAS-58 Talon[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Decreased sway modifier from 1.2 to 1[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][\/p][p][b]GP-31 Grenade Pistol[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Decreased sway modifier from 1.2 to 1[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]LAS-7 Dagger[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Decreased sway modifier from 1.2 to 1[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]P-113 Verdict[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Decreased sway modifier from 1.2 to 1[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]M6C\/SOCOM Pistol[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Decreased sway modifier from 1.2 to 1[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]PLAS-15 Loyalist[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Decreased sway modifier from 1.2 to 1[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]P-11 Stim Pistol[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Decreased sway modifier from 1.2 to 1[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]SG-22 Bushwhacker[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Decreased sway modifier from 1.3 to 1[\/p][\/*][*][p]Move the \u201cVolley\/Semi mode\u201d weapon function from Right to Left weapon function direction [\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]P-4 Senator[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Decreased sway modifier from 1.3 to 1[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]GP-20 Ultimatum[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Decreased sway modifier from 1.3 to 1[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]CQC-30 Stun Baton[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Increased damage from 50 to 75[\/p][\/*][*][p]Increased durable damage from 25 to 38[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]CQC-19 Stun Lance[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Increased damage from 110 to 165[\/p][\/*][*][p]Increased durable damage from 55 to 83[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]CQC-2 Saber[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Increased damage from 125 to 188[\/p][\/*][*][p]Increased durable damage from 65 to 98[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]CQC-5 Combat Hatches[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Increased damage from 160 to 240[\/p][\/*][*][p]Increased durable damage from 80 to 120[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]CQC-42 Machete[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Increased damage from 200 to 300[\/p][\/*][*][p]Increased durable damage from 100 to 150[\/p][\/*][\/list][h3][b]Throwables\n[\/b]\n[img src=\"{STEAM_CLAN_IMAGE}\/44156989\/fb272bacd3e3b657c247a1117d5411ebb52aa8dd.jpg\"][\/img][\/h3][p][b]G-7 Pineapple[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Increased max amount uses 3 to 4[\/p][\/*][*][p]Increased start amount uses 2 to 3[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]G-31 Arc[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Increased max amount uses 4 to 5[\/p][\/*][*][p]Increased start amount uses 3 to 4[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][\/p][h3][b]Stratagems[\/b]\u00a0[\/h3][p]\n[b]SH-20 Ballistic Shield Backpack[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Shorter cooldown from 300 to 240 sec[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]Orbital Smoke Strike[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Shorter cooldown from 100 to 75 sec[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]CQC-9 Defoliation Tool[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Increased damage from 300 to 450[\/p][\/*][*][p]Increased durable damage from 150 to 225[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]CQC-1 One True Flag[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Increased damage from 110 to 200[\/p][\/*][*][p]Increased durable damage from 55 to 100 [\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]RS-422 Railgun[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Move the \u201cSafe\/Unsafe mode\u201d weapon function from Right to Left weapon function direction[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]StA-X3 W.A.S.P. Launcher[\/b] [\/p][list][*][p]Move the \u201cProgrammable ammo mode\u201d weapon function from Right to Left weapon function direction [\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]GL-21 Grenade Launcher[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Increased armor penetration level from Medium to Heavy[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][\/p][h3][b]Armor passives[\/b][\/h3][p][\/p][h3][img src=\"{STEAM_CLAN_IMAGE}\/44156989\/3dc63103446408a39498141f8f6d8e224019ff73.jpg\"][\/img][\/h3][p][\/p][p][b]Peak Physique[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Decreased melee damage bonus from 100% to 40%[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]Rock Solid[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Decreased melee damage bonus from 100% to 40%[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]Reinforced Epaulettes[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Decreased melee damage bonus from 50% to 20%[\/p][p][\/p][\/*][\/list][h2]Enemies[\/h2][p][b]General[\/b][\/p][p]\n[\/p][p]Some enemies have had their damage vs durable rebalanced to adjust for Helldiver vehicles with large health pools. It will not change their effectiveness against normal Helldivers, only their vehicles.[\/p][p]\n[\/p][p]Things like attacks from Bile Titans, Chargers, Crescent Overseers, Overseers, Rocket firing Automatons, Hulk melee attacks, mortars, acid etc have gotten values adjusted. Some of the adjustments only affect certain targets (ie the Bastion). Other adjustments also affect the FRV and Exosuits.[\/p][p]\n[\/p][p]Enemies Aim calculations were not always updated when there were many enemies trying to aim, making Automatons on higher difficulties a bit bad at aiming. They should now attempt to update the aim better considering the data they have before they get another proper aim update. This means that Automatons will aim better even when there are a lot of them without any further cost to performance.[\/p][h3]\n\n[b]Terminids[\/b][\/h3][p][\/p][p][b]Dragon roach[\/b][\/p][p][\/p][list][*][p]lowered the direct damage from the flame attack by 25%[\/p][\/*][\/list][h3]\n[b]Automatons[\/b] [\/h3][p][\/p][p][b]Rocket Raider[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Rockets now deals increased damage vs Durable targets[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]Devastator[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Removed durable on arms[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]Rocket Devastator[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Rockets now deals increased damage vs Durable targets[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]Hulk Bruiser[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Rockets now deals increased damage vs Durable targets[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]Gunship[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]updated its targeting software and should now be better at hitting their targets[\/p][\/*][*][p]Rockets now deals increased damage vs Durable targets[\/p][p][\/p][\/*][\/list][h3][b]Illuminate[\/b][\/h3][p]\n[b]Overseer[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Overseer`s weapon now deals increased damage vs Durable targets[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]Crescent Overseer[\/b] [\/p][list][*][p]Increased force on artillery attack to stagger the Helldiver[\/p][\/*][*][p]Increased the damage of its direct shot attack[\/p][\/*][*][p]Crescent Overseer`s weapon now deals increased damage vs Durable targets[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][\/p][h2]\ud83c\udfae [b]Gameplay[\/b][\/h2][p]\n[\/p][p][b]Emotes and Victory poses[\/b][\/p][p][\/p][p]Emotes and victory poses are now interchangeable. Except for a few exceptions like emotes that require 2 people, the kick and a few others, all the victory poses can now be used as emotes and all emotes can now be used as victory poses[\/p][h2]\n\ud83d\udd27 [b]Fixes[\/b][\/h2][p]\n[\/p][p][b]Hang Detection[\/b][\/p][p][\/p][p]As part of our ongoing war against bugs and instability we have introduced a \u201chang detection\u201d feature in the PC version. If the game hangs (freezes) for more than 20 seconds then this new feature will crash the game instead of letting it stay hung. This generates a file called a \u201ccrash dump\u201d which contains important debugging information for our programmers to diagnose and fix the root cause of the hang.\u00a0[\/p][p]\nIf you experience a hang, please wait at least 40 seconds before restarting your PC to allow the hang detector to do its job.\u00a0[\/p][p]\nIf you experience a 20+ second hang followed by a crash:[\/p][p]\n[\/p][list][*][p]If the crash reporting window shows up then please submit the report as usual.\u00a0[\/p][\/*][*][p]If the crash reporting window doesn\u2019t show up (it can fail), we humbly request that you share the crash dump file with our player support team ([url=\"https:\/\/arrowhead.zendesk.com\/\"]https:\/\/arrowhead.zendesk.com\/[\/url]). They will be able to assist you in locating and sharing the crash dump 