imation if the player reloads the weapon immediately after firing[\/p][\/*][*][p]When cancelling a reload after a new projectile was made visible, but before it was put into the weapon; the weapon would display the new shell in the weapon, even with the weapon empty. The weapons will now correctly display if it is ready to fire or not[\/p][\/*][*][p]Heat based weapons are now displaying overheating properly, in the Weapon Function Menu[\/p][\/*][*][p]Kills with \"One True Flag\" will now count towards Major Order kills[\/p][\/*][*][p]Fixed the M-1000 Maxigun wind-up sounds which would sometimes not play properly[\/p][\/*][*][p]Player can no longer throw multiple stratagems after entering and exiting emplacements[\/p][\/*][*][p]Grenade launcher shots and explosions from AR\/GL-21 One-Two rifle should now be visible when shot by other players[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][\/p][p][b]P-92 Warrant[\/b][\/p][p][\/p][list][*][p]Made the drag and gravity the same on the non-guided projectile as the last patch change for the guided projectile.[\/p][\/*][\/list][list][*][p]Move the \u201cGuided mode\/None Guided mode\u201d weapon function from Right to Left weapon function direction[\/p][\/*][*][p]Fixed its crosshair not updating when toggling its weapon function through the new input bindings\n[\/p][p][\/p][\/*][\/list][p][b]Enemies[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Enemies have learned how to target better[\/p][\/*][*][p]Fixed spawn rate on Rapid Acquisition missions on difficulty CR7-10. Adjusted spawn points on Rapid Acquisition map[\/p][\/*][\/list][p][\/p][p][b]Miscellaneous Fixes[\/b][\/p][list][*][p]Automaton dropships will now move less erratically when dropping enemies[\/p][\/*][*][p]Fix incorrect camera positioning when transitioning to first person while reloading[\/p][\/*][*][p]Fixed an issue where players could land on Command Bunkers in city missions[\/p][\/*][*][p]Fixed certain items not being interactable inside specific PoIs on Magma planets[\/p][\/*][*][p]Solved terrain height c